The authors of  75 coined the concept of survivability as the fraction of initial conditions giving rise to evolutions that stay within a desirable region of the state space all the time. This concept is similar but different from that of the tracking probability since we only compare initial and final states. The tracking probability \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
